data.description: Country living in north Lakeland on over an acre with NO HOA. This is a lovely 5 acre property that is difficult to come by, and the chance is calling your name!!! This 5 acre north Lakeland property has 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. This might be a great beginner home or rental property, or it could be an ideal place to live while you develop your dream home or barndominium project. Imagine walking out your back door to hunt deer, turkey, and wild pigs on your own farm! Horses allowed; great, huge yard for dirt bikes/go carting; great yard for star gazing & to watch rocket launches at the Cape... bonfires.... Tree lined west property line.  Quiet neighbors.  Private setting. Make your own private showing appointment today, before it's too late.
